abstract: Mr. and Mrs. John Alfred Davenport of New York have announced the engagement of their daughter, Miss Susan Wheeler Davenport, to Piers Brooke of London and New York. He is the son of Lady Mabel Cheetham of Eyford Park in Gloucestershire, England, and Richard Brooke of Hamburg, Germany.
